e issues which I have outlined in this case, and the manner in which the parties have approached this appeal, it would not be appropriate to make any order as to costs.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s3\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af5\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f5\fs24\lang1033\loch\f5\fs24\lang1033 
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s3\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af5\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f5\fs24\lang1033\loch\f5\fs24\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f5\fs24\lang1033\i0\b0 For these reasons the following order is made:}
