\par \pard\plain {\listtext\pard\plain \li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-360\f5\lang1033\f4\fs24\f5\lang1025\sl360\slmult1\qj 3.\tab}\ilvl0 \ltrpar\s3\sl360\slmult1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ls2\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi-360\rtlch\af5\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af4\langfe255\hich\f5\fs24\lang1033\loch\f5\fs24\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f5\fs24\lang1033\i0\b0 The chairperson of the Tribunal is requested to ensure that the application of first respondent to intervene be heard as a matter of urgency.}
